des:
The Vegan Adventures skill is an awesome way to improve the health and lifestyle of the aging population. Sustain a healthy plant based diet over time. This skill will take you to the Vegan Adventures Challenge website. Try it with any Alexa compatible mobile phone, or an Alexa hands-free phone!

With this skill, Alexa can help you: Ok.
For a reminder of a few things you can do with the Skill, you can ask, "Alexa, what can I say in vegan adventures?"
